name: Dungeon Reset
author: Ant Studio,Daul
short_description: Once a Dungeon has been explored and its traps were activated, it resets itself for the next \u2018users\u2019. But those resets don\u2019t apply to me?! The only existence that has become free in the endlessly resetting dungeon.
description: Once a Dungeon has been explored and its traps were activated, it resets itself for the next \u2018users\u2019. But those resets don\u2019t apply to me?! The only existence that has become free in the endlessly resetting dungeon. Armed with absolute grinding, Jeong Dawoon \u2018the Bug\u2019 begins his dungeon exploration!

name: Trash of the Count’s Family
altName: TCF / Trash Count / 백작가의 망나니가 되었다 / 成为伯爵家的混混
author: Elegant Yoo Ryeo Han
short_description: When I opened my eyes, I was inside a novel. [The Birth of a Hero].
description: When I opened my eyes, I was inside a novel. [The Birth of a Hero].  [The Birth of a Hero] was a novel focused on the adventures of the main character, Choi Han – a high school boy from Earth who was transported to a different dimension – alongside other numerous, rising heroes of the continent. I became a part of that novel as the trash of the Count’s family, the family that oversaw the territory where the first village that Choi Han visits is located.  Choi Han became vengeful after that village was destroyed by a mysterious group of assailants, and grew incensed after he reported the matter to the Count’s son and got brushed off. He gets beaten to a pulp.  “…This is going to be a problem.”  But, I feel like it is worth trying to make this my new life regardless.
